		<description><![CDATA[Before fluency: Play music Skim books Do SRS reps Hear and understand more than you speak Read more than you write After fluency: Play music Skim books Do SRS reps Hear and understand more than you speak Read more than you write Also, enlightenment .]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Before fluency:</p>
<ul>
<li>Play music</li>
<li>Skim books</li>
<li>Do SRS reps</li>
<li>Hear and understand more than you speak</li>
<li>Read more than you write</li>
</ul>
<p>After fluency:</p>
<ul>
<li>Play music</li>
<li>Skim books</li>
<li>Do SRS reps</li>
<li>Hear and understand more than you speak</li>
<li>Read more than you write</li>
</ul>
